Text: I am traveling to the a European country which is called Portugal, this would
  not only a big opportunity for exchanging cultures but having new experience of
  green continent people thoughts and familiarizing them would be a great fortune
  for me and, I am from a country by the name of Afghanistan as I am in my society
  I realized that the young generation of this country is deeply eager to meet Europeans
  and use their ideas and Creativeness for self life and using the method of being
  success and know what is the success that Europe has great writers especially Portugal,
  the second reason that want to choose this travel is knowing what is the great secrets
  of Europe  that we has a great economic condition.
